PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Public Works and Government Services of ROSE MARIE MacDONALD, of Little Pond, Prince Edward Island, as a director of the Board of Directors of Canada Mortgage and Housing Corporation to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Patricia Toner, whose term has expired.
